Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.50,0:00:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels like the sky's about to suck me right in.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.37,0:00:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They call this a sky full of falling stars.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.10,0:00:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! A shooting star!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.22,0:00:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.25,0:00:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond that one, there's another star.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.22,0:00:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Space just goes on forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.30,0:00:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda makes you realize \Nhow small people really are.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.01,0:01:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit acting so modest.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.13,0:01:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the great Batsu, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.23,0:01:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Young aspirations swell up \Nwhere it counts, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.91,0:01:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh—\NThe hell, man?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.07,0:01:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to keep your jokes to yourself, dammit! {なにすんだこら、冗談は顔だけにしろっていつも言ってんだろ。}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.79,0:01:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, that's something else...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.79,0:01:14.30,Overlap,,0,0,0,,What if it becomes a habit? {(小声)くせになったらどうすんだよ」}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.53,0:01:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Dammit...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.00,0:01:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at all these stars makes \Nthe daily grind feel devastatingly pointless.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.71,0:01:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel devastated as hell right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.83,0:01:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, another shooting star.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.93,0:01:30.58,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.58,0:01:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a wish before it burns out!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.11,0:01:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late, it's gone.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.47,0:01:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, another one!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.78,0:01:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a woman! I want a woman! I want a woman!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.02,0:01:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.71,0:01:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunio!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.45,0:01:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.74,0:02:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dammit, Koshien's on the line...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.48,0:02:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, fight!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.65,0:02:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanasaki! Where are Batsu and Terry?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.29,0:02:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they think this game is?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.23,0:02:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Koshien's at stake!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.13,0:02:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll come. I believe in them.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.00,0:02:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.54,0:02:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.50,0:02:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Heroes show up fashionably late...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.27,0:02:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Told you so.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.74,0:04:42.99,Thought,,0,0,0,,Yoo-hoo, Kunio!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.45,0:04:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.49,0:04:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.46,0:04:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.41,0:04:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Anne?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.79,0:04:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Clumsy me...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.87,0:04:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.83,0:05:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I just love riding the bike.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.73,0:05:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-daa!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.61,0:05:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.04,0:05:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.79,0:05:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one of us are you asking?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.33,0:05:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunio! You're pushing it too hard! {/entering the corner too fast}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.85,0:05:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Kunio...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.34,0:05:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's bold.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.10,0:06:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What a waste! \NShe could've just given it away. {lit: She could've just said the word [and we'd take it for ourselves] probably?}{テリー\Nバッ\N「おー大胆!」\N「もったいない、ひとこと言ってくれ\Nれば」}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.13,0:06:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.76,0:06:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.80,0:06:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec! What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.10,0:06:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She needs me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.93,0:06:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up. She'll just turn you down.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.35,0:06:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about whether she dumps me or not!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.41,0:06:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You piss me off, you know that? \NWhy don't you go die in a ditch?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.28,0:06:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking for it! {/wanna fight?}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.91,0:06:36.79,Top,,0,0,0,,You bastard! You think you're funny?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.73,Top,,0,0,0,,And you think you're a hit with the ladies?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.73,0:06:39.38,Top,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.38,0:06:41.80,Top,,0,0,0,,She needs someone kind and sensitive right now.{???? no clue, these background lines aren't in the script}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.00,0:06:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, girl, what're you doing out here?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How about going out with us?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.91,0:06:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a brand-new ride. Let's go for a spin.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.11,0:06:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, don't play hard to get.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.19,0:06:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,At least talk to us a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.26,0:06:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where you headed?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.47,0:06:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll give you a lift.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.24,0:06:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.89,0:07:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on, hang out with us, why don't you!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.85,0:07:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?! Let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.84,0:07:04.48,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Relax, it's just for a sec. C'mon.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.47,0:07:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.97,0:07:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold it right there—whoa! {??? not in the script}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.35,0:07:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.31,0:07:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You prick!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.45,0:07:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.44,0:07:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, sunshine.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.96,0:07:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tacchan!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.57,0:07:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Battery... {combination of Batsu & Terry because battery (batting and pitching) is what they do and a specific term: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Battery_(baseball)}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.17,0:07:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Crooked Tacchan, \NSnap-in-Half-Tacchan is here! {曲がりのタッちゃん、ポッキンタッちゃんでーす}{about his dick probably; no idea what pokkin is but most likely it implies that his dick is crooked and looks like it's folded }
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.44,0:07:27.40,Top,,0,0,0,,Kyaa! Gross! {from script: わ~、きゃー、やだーきもちわる}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.86,0:07:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Still crooked as ever, huh? {think in this case it's also about his behavior?}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.27,0:07:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Crooked, crooked!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.72,0:07:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it! You bastards ruined a perfect moment!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.58,0:07:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Snap-in-Half-Tacchan, Snap-in-Half-Tacchan!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.41,0:07:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuo-san, who the hell are these guys?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.41,0:07:43.88,Top,,0,0,0,,Ah, Snapped-in-Half! I'm so Snapped-in-Half!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.67,0:07:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.22,0:07:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna hear Tatsuo's little secret?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.03,0:07:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell do you want?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.20,0:07:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,See, this real important thing of his is—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.08,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Shut your mouth, you rat bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.47,0:07:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, poor guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yoshio, you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.49,0:07:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That was slick back there. {/cool}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.97,0:08:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.67,0:08:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshio...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.27,0:08:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Though maybe you jumped the gun a little. {/that was a rash decision}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a long hike to the station from here.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.65,0:08:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You punks!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.45,0:08:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And that heap of a car won't get you far.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.79,0:08:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the same guy I used to be.\NI'll give you a taste of hell!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.56,0:08:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no worries as long as we're around.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.01,0:08:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Bachan! {batsu-chan}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.03,0:08:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out, this guy's dangerous.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.52,0:08:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking—\Nyour dirty little motives are showing!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.52,0:08:23.39,Top,,0,0,0,,Y-You lookin' down on me?! You pricks...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.93,0:08:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You punks! Quit standin' around—waste 'em!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.03,0:08:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but hang tight a sec.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.03,0:08:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! You swine! {terry's lines}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.03,0:08:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you'd hit a lady?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.27,0:08:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.22,0:08:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you savages doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.66,0:08:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this, Tatsuo—\Nditching baseball to go pro in boxing?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.39,0:08:52.89,Top,,0,0,0,,Jackass... {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.76,Top,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.71,0:09:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew... Not again!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.96,0:09:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel good pounding on your cute little lackeys?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.82,0:09:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You brats are dead meat!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.64,0:09:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how's that? Straightened you out a little?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.76,0:09:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I kinda feel sorry for your lackeys—\Nletting such a wimp boss them around.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.87,0:09:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! W-Whatcha doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.79,0:09:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, hey, hey! Cut it out! Stop! Stop, dammit!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.77,0:09:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oopsie-daisy...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.09,0:09:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hop on?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who are you? {dunno, maybe asking what are you doing, maybe "where will you ride"}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.63,0:09:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a special seat reserved for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.04,0:10:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Batsu!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.58,0:10:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm Terry! \NDidn't catch your name last time—what is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.50,0:10:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.61,0:10:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? Couldn't hear ya! {because her name is just two letters in japanese - "an"}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.33,0:10:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne. My name's Anne.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.25,0:10:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshio, Kazu—how long you gonna lie there?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.13,0:10:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.86,0:10:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get off, you idiots!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.69,0:10:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.39,0:10:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Hold on!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.97,0:10:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold still! Don't move a muscle! \NOne wrong move and I'm finished!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.58,0:10:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, the heavens sure got it in for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.11,0:10:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right when we're about to start our youth, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.29,0:10:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess they're jealous of us.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.55,0:10:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn sky, screw you!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.24,0:10:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop here a sec.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.25,0:10:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.03,0:11:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got things to do. Thanks for the ride.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.89,0:11:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that so coldly.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us take you home!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.30,0:11:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you two!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.38,0:11:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, we came for our lost piece of youth. {lit: forgotten thing of the youth (seishun)}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.64,0:11:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Come watch us play baseball tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.41,0:11:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Baseball?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, believe it or not, \Nwe're high school ballplayers.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.50,0:11:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You two?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.85,0:11:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What, is that weird?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.18,0:11:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the star pitcher!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.89,0:11:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's the catcher who squats like he's shitting.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, your mouth is filthy.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.93,0:11:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then squat properly, will ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.69,0:11:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really like baseball.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.47,0:11:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.51,0:11:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you lost something last week, \Nyou'll need to go to the Enoshima head office.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.20,0:11:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not last week—youth!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.23,0:11:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to get all dramatic about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.77,0:11:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A lost piece of youth...{same as before}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Our promise tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.01,0:11:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.11,0:12:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, one o'clock!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.57,0:12:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,At Hodogaya Baseball Stadium! {https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%A5%9E%E5%A5%88%E5%B7%9D%E7%9C%8C%E7%AB%8B%E4%BF%9D%E5%9C%9F%E3%82%B1%E8%B0%B7%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E7%A1%AC%E5%BC%8F%E9%87%8E%E7%90%83%E5%A0%B4}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.28,0:12:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick with us and every day'll be brighter.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.60,0:12:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll clear away the rain \Nand the clouds in your heart too!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.56,0:12:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Let's have some fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.09,0:12:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, next!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.94,0:12:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.30,0:12:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your back into it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.57,0:12:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.47,0:12:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.51,0:12:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, everyone's out there covered in\Nmud practicing, and those two are slacking off again.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.97,0:12:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,As their homeroom teacher, it's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.12,0:12:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Always late, always sneaking out early,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.25,0:12:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,disrespecting teachers, no charm at all...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.13,0:12:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they even think school is? Ugh, my stomach... {/ouch}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.63,0:12:58.55,Overlap,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.55,0:13:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's those two! Just thinking \Nabout them lately makes my gut hurt.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop whining.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.22,0:13:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Our school might make it to Koshien for the first time since its founding.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.66,0:13:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's thanks to Batto Gun and Ichimonji Teru.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.18,0:13:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your stomachache doesn't amount to squat.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.79,0:13:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Doesn't amount to squat?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.27,0:13:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, Chairman, if our school's star battery \Nis always acting like a pair of delinquents...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.72,0:13:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Principal, surely you've got something to say.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.10,0:13:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, Vice Principal, Kito—let it be.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.89,0:13:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're young, you stray off the rails a little. \NIsn't that right, Chairman?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.46,0:13:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.27,0:13:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kito-sensei! Kito-sensei!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We love you!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Smooch, smooch!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.66,0:13:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the fall of education!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.93,0:14:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That was mighty brave of her—\Nhow that girl tossed her bike. {gallant; manly; brave; imposing; awe-inspiring; chivalrous; dignified}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.04,0:14:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.49,0:14:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I bet deep down she's really hurting. \NI got that feeling.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.42,0:14:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So even you can read a girl's feelings sometimes?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.29,0:14:30.54,Top,,0,0,0,,{fuck knows, not in the script}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.45,0:14:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm the only one who can get her back on her feet. She looked at me that way.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.23,0:14:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What way?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.16,0:14:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Like she fell for me at first sight \Nand was begging me to do whatever I wanted.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.56,0:14:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You've lost it. Here—pick one.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.58,0:14:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What the hell's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.76,0:14:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's there?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.09,0:14:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you drew "X." \NThat settles it—Anne's my girl. {ペケ (peke) = failure; futility; uselessness; no good}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.91,0:14:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What "X"?! Don't hand me that crap.\NYou made this stupid thing up!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.76,0:14:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let it get you down.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.61,0:14:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, let me see the other one.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.67,0:15:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.78,0:15:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You cheated as usual! \NI've hated that about you since forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.30,0:15:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose your cool over some dumb crap.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.27,0:15:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You two keep fighting like that \Nand you won't make it to Koshien.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.87,0:15:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"You two?" {dunno what's he so surprised about, not like kirishima is saying it any special way}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.54,0:15:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look, it's "You Two" Onishima.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.86,0:15:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Not "Onishima," it's Kirishima! \NThat thing looks good on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.37,0:15:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And where's Megumi-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.91,0:15:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad for you, my sis is out shopping.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.72,0:15:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So your target's Batsu's sister, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.27,0:15:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this guy's been grinding it out chasing her.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.92,0:15:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And she hasn't dumped him yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.47,0:15:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis is running a business here, \Nso she has no choice but to serve him coffee.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.99,0:15:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Figures. A grumpy middle-aged biker \Nlike him isn't exactly a chick magnet.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.96,0:15:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No shit—he dresses like he pulled \Nhis clothes out of a chest at random! {tansu is a "chest of drawers / dresser" so idk, assuming he just compares him to the furniture? tansu is probably because of 桐たんす - line at 16:08}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.72,0:15:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys got some nerve.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.91,0:15:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize what'll happen if you mess with Traffic Officer Kirishima, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.45,0:15:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, uncle Onishima...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.22,0:15:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirishima-san is manly, \Nlame, and dazzling all at once.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.38,0:16:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Look here! \NQuit goofing around with that "Oni" stuff!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.29,0:16:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Onishima-san, welcome.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.42,0:16:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Megumi-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.69,0:16:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, please, you know it's Kirishima.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.03,0:16:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please remember for when we marry: "Kiri" as in "chest," \Nand "shima" as in "island nation." {lit: when I take you as bride, it's kiri from kiri drawer, and shima as in island nation}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.12,0:16:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm so sorry! \NI said that without thinking...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.64,0:16:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because these kids are always goofing off.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.31,0:16:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? Oh, not at all—when you're young, \Nyou're always full of energy.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.19,0:16:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, if you mess with me once more, \NI'll slap you with a mountain of tickets. {meaning traffic tickets}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.05,0:16:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{You better be ready! }It's about time you start acting like adults!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.91,0:16:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, aren't they cute little rascals?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.45,0:16:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huff, huff... {「はっふっ、はっふっ」}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.66,0:17:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, getting double-teamed in this game—what the hell?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.23,0:17:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit-for-brains!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.27,0:17:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Tatsuo-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.77,0:17:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.44,0:17:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem? \NYou think it's funny I'm crooked?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.67,0:17:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Crooked, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.03,0:17:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Assholes!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.04,0:18:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.79,0:18:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just trying to help, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.71,0:18:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's up with you, Tatsuo-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.75,0:18:10.62,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those two sure have a real fighting spirit within them.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.62,0:18:12.24,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you think, Kashino-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.24,0:18:14.42,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yep, they really have fight... {todo as well}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell's watching this crap?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.71,0:18:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll turn it off.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.52,0:18:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said to turn it off?! Answer me, you punk!\NWhy do you think you can do whatever you want?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.83,0:18:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokai University Sumo! {name of their team}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.29,0:18:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{dosukoi is a staple chant associated with sumo; can't be assed to sub all of it tbh so not even gonna bother}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.26,0:18:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they really gonna do that every time?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.65,0:18:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the Kokugikan Sumo Arena, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.41,0:18:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.33,0:18:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see her.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.75,0:18:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.73,0:18:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she hates baseball.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.81,0:18:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she hates you, actually.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.44,0:18:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are your ears broken?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.85,0:18:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your face broken?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.96,0:18:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got your hands all over her breasts \N‘cause of your obvious intentions.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.19,0:18:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's ever touched her breasts?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.21,0:18:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a sharp eye!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.47,0:18:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Battery!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.12,0:19:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we done talking? \NThe other batter's already in the ring. {as in sumo ring}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.93,0:19:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Batsu, focus!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.59,0:19:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's knock them all out of the ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead ball!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.97,0:19:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stick that huge belly over the base!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.18,0:19:26.37,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Batto-kun must be really frustrated, \Nhe's thrashing around on the mound.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.75,0:19:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He runs!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.52,0:19:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Batsu! {sounds more like mazui and batsu can't do much here anyway but it's batsu in the script?}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.52,0:19:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Safe!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.46,0:19:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop running so noisily! \NYou're distracting me! Jeez...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.07,0:20:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Crud...!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's outta here.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice one. {ちゃんちゃん not sure what to make of this onoma}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.53,0:20:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Hey, grab it! \NThat one in the middle.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.13,0:20:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha! Oh! Still warm from Yoko's boobs!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.93,0:20:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.08,0:20:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Miko!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.36,0:20:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.97,0:20:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.66,0:20:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.91,0:20:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling good?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.33,0:20:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, look! I finally bought it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.15,0:20:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The brand new GSX400X Impulse! \NI worked part-time like mad for six months to get it. {dunno what she means by "there"}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.02,0:20:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I kept messing up, \Nso I was shy to show my face. {means "during riding"}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.33,0:20:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Next, we're touring to Izu! \NYou should come too, Anne!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.27,0:20:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.11,0:20:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.48,0:20:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I... gave up my bike. {/threw away}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.33,0:20:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really? That's a waste!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.79,0:21:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because of what happened to Kunio?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.61,0:21:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sacchi!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.83,0:21:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.22,0:21:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine. Maybe I acted on impulse, though...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.27,0:21:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.99,0:21:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You feeling down?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.25,0:21:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm okay. Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.63,0:21:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll ride again sometime.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.14,0:21:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! And next time, you lead the pack!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.13,0:21:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta go now. Everyone ride safe!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.89,0:21:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The game's moving surprisingly slowly.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.07,0:21:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't do something crazy, would she?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.46,0:21:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because her boyfriend flew off a cliff, \Ndoesn't mean she's the type to go flying too.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.71,0:21:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's kick things into gear.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.82,0:21:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. I'm gonna hit one out of the park.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.16,0:21:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Strike!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.66,0:21:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.86,0:21:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Terry swung and missed!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.61,0:21:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A screwball? {変化球}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.33,0:21:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a fastball?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.34,0:21:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on with them today?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.12,0:22:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really strange.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.24,0:22:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just their real level. \NExpecting more was a mistake.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.17,0:22:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We've spoiled them way too much...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.41,0:22:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not aiming at us, are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.47,0:22:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Those two would totally do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.15,0:22:18.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,Not a straight pitch...\NIt's curving right at the edge of the base.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.42,0:22:21.89,Thought,,0,0,0,,Hit it in front of the base!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.20,0:22:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.54,0:22:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch, no good?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.82,0:22:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.55,0:22:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it, Terry!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:50.58,0:22:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Out!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:55.08,0:22:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So I didn't make it.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:56.27,0:22:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:57.88,0:23:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he didn't even flinch at Terry's slide.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:01.28,0:23:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys really throw you off your game.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.14,0:23:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:04.07,0:23:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A shame to waste this game...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:07.85,0:23:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're thinking...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:09.28,0:23:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's exactly what I think. Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.01,0:23:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:14.02,0:23:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:16.64,0:23:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got important business. \NWe're heading out.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:19.46,0:23:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, we're in the middle of a game!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:21.46,0:23:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Handle it yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:22.89,0:23:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! We're losing by two points!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.09,0:23:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for Koshien! Koshien!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.80,0:23:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got something \Nway more important than Koshien.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.35,0:23:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"More important," huh? \NYou're just off to hit on girls!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:34.76,0:23:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insist on leaving with your back to the enemy, \Nyou'll need to go through me first.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:39.93,0:23:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean that?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:41.58,0:23:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with the main characters' pace. {「主人公のペース乱すんじゃねえ!」 but idk what he means, maybe it's a meta joke that they've gotta be elsewhere now as the movie characters?}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:50.45,0:23:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:52.65,0:23:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:53.66,0:23:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope the weather's nice tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:03.71,0:24:11.26,Top,,0,0,0,,{no chance}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:04.59,0:24:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Still here, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:08.11,0:24:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's do this.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:12.62,0:24:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings! {some other typical sumo stock phrase, don't care}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.19,0:24:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to stay back as much as possible.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:16.27,0:24:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hanasaki-kun, do you have the data \Non these fatsos' relief pitching? {??? tlc, no clue what's this sheftori}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.43,0:24:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Tokai Sumo Team, \Nno relief pitchers. {/high school}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:25.61,0:24:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:27.15,0:24:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no pitcher?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:37.27,0:24:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Strike!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:38.73,0:24:40.29,Thought,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:45.07,0:24:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he planning?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:46.55,0:24:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Deadly Repeated Balls-Crushing Syndrome! {必殺デッドタマタマシンドローム dunno exactly how many layers there are to this joke}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:50.91,0:24:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Deadly Repeated Balls-Crushing Syndrome?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:58.71,0:25:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye now!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:03.65,0:25:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it! Back in middle school, \Nhe pulled this off on me too and made it snap in half! {pokkin}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:07.78,0:25:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:09.00,0:25:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll live...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:13.49,0:25:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Terry, gimme one big hit! {probably "for when it's your turn at bat"}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:16.50,0:25:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That stubborn pitcher \Nwon't go down with just one.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:21.35,0:25:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Play ball! {or just "play"}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:38.20,0:25:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he... die?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:41.73,0:25:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanasaki, you're up!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:43.43,0:25:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:45.06,0:25:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Can you do it?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:49.53,0:25:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What? He's still got the guts?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:54.83,0:25:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Umpire! Pinch-hitter Hanasaki, taking the field!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:57.36,0:25:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:00.68,0:26:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:02.66,0:26:05.59,Thought,,0,0,0,,Those two already made it to base, \Nso I gotta help too! {せっかくあの二人が塁に出たんだ。何とかするぞ!}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:06.13,0:26:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanasaki! Strike the pitcher! \NRight back at him!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:29.17,0:26:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he's alive...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:30.15,0:26:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, Hanasaki!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:31.63,0:26:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You did great! Keep running! {「お前はえらい! 回れ、回れ!」}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:33.61,0:26:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sera! Back home, back home! {「バックホーム! バックホーム!」}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:36.11,0:26:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The ball's stuck! I can't get it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:38.99,0:26:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:40.28,0:26:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, one point! {i assume it's the umpire speaking}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:41.35,0:26:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Sera!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:47.40,0:26:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I got this!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:56.95,0:26:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Safe!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:02.56,0:27:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I need a favor, Kacchan! {カッちゃん - no clue if it's a proper name or he/she really is his mother}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:32.28,0:27:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Gonna throw your own body off there next?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:37.95,0:27:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:39.01,0:27:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't come to the game.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:40.93,0:27:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wanted to show it to you. \NToday was quite funny.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:43.79,0:27:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about baseball.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:46.79,0:27:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Our baseball isn't ordinary. {hanpa = half-assed}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:49.37,0:27:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They call it "feel-good baseball."
Dialogue: 10,0:27:52.88,0:27:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, baseball aside, let's ride.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:57.76,0:27:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's feel the wind!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:09.68,0:28:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't get enough of this feeling!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:12.36,0:28:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm buzzing too! {binbin is also "rock-hard"}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:14.00,0:28:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Buzzing?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:14.67,0:28:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, buzzing!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:15.73,0:28:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been buzzing forever!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:17.65,0:28:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Buzz, buzz, buzz, buzz. {assuming he's doing something to make the bike veer}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:26.84,0:28:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! {orya}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:31.71,0:28:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh oh, think we'll fall?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:44.13,0:28:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! {gomen yo}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:47.16,0:28:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That's one sturdy roof, \Nas expected of a British car! {「がんじょうな屋根、さすが英国車。\N調子ん乗ってもう一発行くか!」}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:50.33,0:28:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling the buzz, \Nso how about another go? {/riding the momentum}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:02.64,0:29:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne! Hold on tight!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:07.95,0:29:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Batsu!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:08.56,0:29:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:10.52,0:29:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Buzzing... {電撃}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:12.47,0:29:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuttle Loop!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:14.47,0:29:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:15.65,0:29:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:17.40,0:29:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:29.57,0:29:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it slow. Check your surroundings.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:31.39,0:29:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:32.89,0:29:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry, we actually needed to go that way! My bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:35.27,0:29:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Whoa.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:36.67,0:29:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, just make a U-turn!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:38.08,0:29:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem! {nanno}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:39.84,0:29:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I shouldn't push you like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:42.55,0:29:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:49.15,0:29:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So? How was it riding in the back for the first time?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:51.21,0:29:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:52.35,0:29:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty solid, right? My driving.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:54.95,0:29:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say it's passable.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:57.13,0:29:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:01.39,0:30:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Batsu!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:02.43,0:30:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:03.23,0:30:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Onishima! Get off!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:06.01,0:30:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:14.65,0:30:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:16.20,0:30:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dirty! Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:18.13,0:30:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:19.47,0:30:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say, punk?!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:20.57,0:30:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What the—
Dialogue: 10,0:30:21.20,0:30:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop it! Stop it! Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:24.80,0:30:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Told you we should've stopped! { 「ボクは反対したんスよ」 lit: I was opposed to it}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:26.26,0:30:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that you, kid? Running a marathon in this heat to aim for Koshien?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:30.67,0:30:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! \NYou being here is why this happened!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:33.42,0:30:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you! \NI'm never letting you into Love Dream again! {their cafe}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:36.94,0:30:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you all of a sudden? \NIt's hot today, are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:40.27,0:30:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Shut up! Shut up! \NI hate you, you swine!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:45.29,0:30:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop!{Am I tripping or are the Be-Bop fellows yelling "Morata" as they leave?}{I hear something but I doubt it's moratta and I don't have any better alternatives}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:47.87,0:30:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! That's obstruction of the law! {obstructing the discharge of official duties; hindering a government official in the execution of his duties}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:50.44,0:30:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never letting you into Love Dream!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:42.00,0:32:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going now.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:58.58,0:33:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Terry! If you're there, prepare yourself! {「テリー、いたら覚悟しろー!」}
Dialogue: 10,0:33:02.01,0:33:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Achoo! Batsu must be cursing me again.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:06.01,0:33:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Anne, you should know that \Neven if you try to forget, it's impossible. {knowing only too well; being fully aware of}
Dialogue: 10,0:33:10.21,0:33:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dwelling on it forever is a waste.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:12.93,0:33:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:15.53,0:33:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you waste your days on nonsense, \Nbefore you know it, you'll be an old lady...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:22.35,0:33:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:24.73,0:33:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:27.15,0:33:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard... Terry!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:30.72,0:33:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you do me dirty!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:32.66,0:33:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye now.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:33.53,0:33:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Wait, w-wait a second!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:36.18,0:33:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You...! You did something to her!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:39.33,0:33:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She hates you, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:42.12,0:33:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make stuff up.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:44.08,0:33:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're noisy, and that's that.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:45.54,0:33:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:46.90,0:33:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing's blasting shit, for starters!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:49.01,0:33:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell, you bastard...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:52.28,0:33:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you whiny bitch! {???? not in the script}
Dialogue: 10,0:33:55.24,0:33:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can beat me?! {????? same}
Dialogue: 10,0:34:08.09,0:34:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat my dust!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:09.24,0:34:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! You shithead!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:23.48,0:34:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne, I'm the only one who can heal your heart!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:28.33,0:34:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cretin! {yokel; bumpkin​}
Dialogue: 10,0:34:29.00,0:34:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:30.74,0:34:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kya! What are you doing out there, Mister?!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:35.01,0:34:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:35.85,0:34:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:36.81,0:34:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:37.21,0:34:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're causing trouble!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:39.45,0:34:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please return to your seat!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:41.71,0:34:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, stop it already! Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:50.36,0:34:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:54.55,0:34:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:56.30,0:34:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You punk!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:00.97,0:35:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being such a nuisance!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:06.12,0:35:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{nothing meaningful acc to the script}{What does the script really say for this bit?}{something like "whoa"}
Dialogue: 10,0:35:09.52,0:35:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! Wait! Wait! Hey! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:18.12,0:35:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:27.48,0:35:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne, even if you try to forget, \Nit's impossible. We both know that. {again this "you're well aware"}
Dialogue: 10,0:35:31.73,0:35:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But dwelling on it forever is a waste. {same words terry said}
Dialogue: 10,0:35:35.88,0:35:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:38.37,0:35:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 10,0:35:39.37,0:35:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And also...
Dialogue: 10,0:35:41.16,0:35:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you waste your youth on nonsense,\Nyou'll turn into an old lady in no time!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:49.63,0:35:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are weird.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:55.30,0:35:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She laughed!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:56.88,0:35:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:00.18,0:36:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe it was closer to just a smile, but still...
Dialogue: 10,0:36:02.72,0:36:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She was exasperated, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:04.70,0:39:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You two!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:08.28,0:39:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Back off!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:09.66,0:39:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:40:03.71,0:40:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's gotten into you today?
Dialogue: 10,0:40:07.84,0:40:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastards don't normally show your true colors, \Nbut you're a complete mess today, aren't you? {いつもなかなかボロ出さないてめーらが、ボロボロのズタズタじゃねーか。 boro wo dasu = to expose one's faults; to have one's defects exposed; to show oneself up     ,,, boroboro = tattered; battered}
Dialogue: 10,0:40:14.18,0:40:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, even though I was impartial to you sometimes,
Dialogue: 10,0:40:17.65,0:40:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you've totally crossed every line today. {まっ、たまには可愛気があっていいがお前らのは、荒っぽくて困る。}
Dialogue: 10,0:40:20.69,0:40:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, here, take this too, \NI found it in my ice cream.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:25.49,0:40:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one stick, though, so you can fight over it, or gift it to a girl—whatever.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:58.44,0:40:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye then.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:00.98,0:41:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:06.82,0:41:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:53.41,0:41:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 10,0:41:54.74,0:41:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:57.87,0:41:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! She's here!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:03.79,0:42:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:04.38,0:42:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:05.42,0:42:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing?! \NThe game's about to start!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:08.88,0:42:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot, we don't have time for that!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:11.88,0:42:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:13.18,0:42:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm taking you to Koshien no matter what! \NI'll drag you onto the field even if it costs me my life!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:18.72,0:42:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne, you made it! \NI didn't think you'd come.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:21.64,0:42:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! It's the semifinals!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:23.65,0:42:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? \NLet's hurry inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:25.69,0:42:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:27.07,0:42:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insist on going, \Nyou'll need to go through me first!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:30.28,0:42:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop with the same old trick.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:32.53,0:42:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hanasaki, who's our opponent today?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:35.24,0:42:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiran.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:36.49,0:42:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiran?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:40.45,0:42:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright everyone, remember! \NThis game is do-or-die! {lit: the game is different/separate - no clue what he means}
Dialogue: 10,0:42:42.87,0:42:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:44.67,0:42:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's with this vibe? \NWhat's with these gloomy faces?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:49.55,0:42:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:50.84,0:42:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:56.97,0:42:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:57.85,0:42:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiran's third baseman.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:00.60,0:43:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Died in a motorcycle accident, apparently.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:29.84,0:43:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Strike!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:31.88,0:43:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Strike two!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:36.14,0:43:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Strike, batter out!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:37.68,0:43:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling fired up all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:39.18,0:43:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be any good if you're not fired up.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:41.52,0:43:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Strike! Batter out!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:48.31,0:43:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm on fire today,
Dialogue: 10,0:43:51.02,0:43:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't intend on stopping!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:53.03,0:43:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne's in the stands, too. \NTime to show off as a man to the fullest!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:57.78,0:43:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:01.33,0:44:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Safe!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:04.16,0:44:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going all out—don't get hurt, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:06.12,0:44:10.00,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Catcher, Ichimonji-kun at bat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:44:08.96,0:44:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne, you saw that? That was Batsu.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:12.71,0:44:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's do this, Terry.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:15.01,0:44:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:17.22,0:44:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:21.60,0:44:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't a pitch for a cleanup batter. {cleanup batter is ichimonji, he's telling that guy "you weren't even trying"}
Dialogue: 10,0:44:24.18,0:44:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Already out of steam in the semifinals? \NShow me what you're made of!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:33.57,0:44:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:35.90,0:44:39.36,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fifth batter—Hanasaki, the third baseman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:44:36.45,0:44:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Anne, this home run is a gift for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:45.75,0:44:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:46.83,0:44:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:47.79,0:44:51.08,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ichimonji-kun's magnificent, daring home run!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:51.08,0:44:55.55,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Such incredible power. But am I the only one \Nwho feels it's a little over-the-top?
Dialogue: 10,0:44:55.55,0:44:59.51,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Plus, their reckless energy is off the charts...
Dialogue: 10,0:44:57.55,0:45:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Those kids are always like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:00.09,0:45:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it disrespectful, with that portrait there? {あの遺影に失礼だと思わないのかしら}
Dialogue: 10,0:45:02.43,0:45:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They're fired up.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:03.68,0:45:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:45:05.35,0:45:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether the other team's holding a mourning photo or not—actually,
Dialogue: 10,0:45:08.77,0:45:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}because{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}they're holding it—\Nthe two of them are on fire. {/portrait}
Dialogue: 10,0:45:12.36,0:45:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, what are those two?
Dialogue: 10,0:45:14.86,0:45:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's their "on fire?"
Dialogue: 10,0:45:16.32,0:45:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{??????? not in the script, probably nothing}
Dialogue: 10,0:45:17.99,0:45:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:20.70,0:45:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:21.74,0:45:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I'd ever let you! {「んを、真似っ!!\Nさせるか――っ!」}
Dialogue: 10,0:45:25.24,0:45:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, where are you throwing?
Dialogue: 10,0:45:29.29,0:45:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Safe!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:30.50,0:45:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's giving it his all.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:31.92,0:45:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:45:44.43,0:45:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Andre-san? {アンドレさん - whatever that name is}
Dialogue: 10,0:45:51.94,0:45:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kacchan! {again, no clue if it's proper name}
Dialogue: 10,0:45:53.56,0:45:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tacchan!
Dialogue: 10,0:46:03.87,0:46:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They're really fired up now.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:06.35,0:46:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's getting interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:07.49,0:46:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. \NHe just hit it by chance off a lucky swing.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:10.66,0:46:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you, trying to comfort me? \NYou're ten years too young for that! {literal, I know this wording sucks but english doesn't have a stock phrase that'd be a good substitute for this}
Dialogue: 10,0:46:16.38,0:46:20.84,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on? Why did Batto Gun suddenly start chasing Hanasaki-kun?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:46:20.84,0:46:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kacchan, can you believe it?
Dialogue: 10,0:46:23.14,0:46:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They're playing baseball too! \NHigh school baseball, and doing all this nonsense!
Dialogue: 10,0:46:28.35,0:46:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were just delinquents, I wouldn't even get this worked up. But it's high school baseball!
Dialogue: 10,0:46:41.40,0:46:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Safe! Safe!
Dialogue: 10,0:46:43.86,0:46:47.53,Top,,0,0,0,,{no clue, some cleanup batter}
Dialogue: 10,0:46:45.16,0:46:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, they'll send the runner no matter what. {something in baseballian, idk what they mean}
Dialogue: 10,0:46:47.99,0:46:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:53.08,0:46:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, let's make it work!
Dialogue: 10,0:46:54.88,0:46:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bunted it! {「うっ! 落ちたっ!」 "dropped/fell" is not normal baseball term so no clue who says this or what he means}
Dialogue: 10,0:46:56.92,0:46:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Second!
Dialogue: 10,0:46:59.55,0:47:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Out!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:04.89,0:47:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A bunt? That cheap tactic won't work on us!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:09.06,0:47:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want points,\Nplay seriously like a man, dammit! {点がほしけりゃ\Nマジで来やがれ!!」}
Dialogue: 10,0:47:14.48,0:47:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{hasshi in script}
Dialogue: 10,0:47:16.98,0:47:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Three outs! {???? in script batsu says "sei" and umpire says "out" but I literally can't hear that here}
Dialogue: 10,0:47:18.48,0:47:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Third out, change!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:21.69,0:47:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt surprisingly bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:47:26.24,0:47:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Lemme see.
Dialogue: 10,0:47:40.92,0:47:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, catch it with your glove!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:43.88,0:47:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:46.34,0:47:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No good, it hit me squarely \Nand hurts like hell. No way I can wear it.
Dialogue: 10,0:47:49.47,0:47:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just force it on. {「無理してかぶっちゃえばいい = wear it even if it hurts}
Dialogue: 10,0:47:51.77,0:47:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not driving anywhere today.
Dialogue: 10,0:47:54.06,0:48:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? So a clumsy guy can't afford a single error?\NThen just quit baseball already! {「えー! へたっぴいがエラーすんのがいけないんじゃない。野球なんかやめちゃえばいいのに」 - ??? lit: It's not the clumsy guy's fault for making errors. He should just quit baseball altogether! - is she calling him clumsy? how is that not his fault?}
Dialogue: 10,0:48:09.03,0:48:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Left-field single to second? Shit!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:13.04,0:48:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A mere single won't cut it! {/getting to second base}
Dialogue: 10,0:48:17.33,0:48:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Safe!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:18.42,0:48:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's embarrassingly bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:48:26.59,0:48:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to aim for a home run! {ザーホームスチールするぞー!」}
Dialogue: 10,0:48:32.01,0:48:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ball!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:37.52,0:48:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ball two!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:38.85,0:48:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me your grit!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:41.06,0:48:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Walking him is lame as hell! {lit: giving (the batter) an "intentional walk"​ is petty bastard}
Dialogue: 10,0:48:43.82,0:48:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You were already riding the waves, \Nbut let it slip away!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:49.11,0:48:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be... He nailed it!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:53.83,0:48:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Three homers in a row! \NStealing all the attention...
Dialogue: 10,0:48:58.29,0:49:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are still not even trying! {lit: method of doing things, that was halfassed}
Dialogue: 10,0:49:03.84,0:49:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:49:06.21,0:49:11.43,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on? Batto and Ichimonji \Napproached the Seiran stands near the third base...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:49:09.68,0:49:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Unforgivable! \NThey're defiling the sacred field!
Dialogue: 10,0:49:19.77,0:49:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:49:21.27,0:49:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are they doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:49:38.66,0:49:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done!
Dialogue: 10,0:49:41.83,0:49:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Hanasaki?
Dialogue: 10,0:49:43.00,0:49:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:49:44.34,0:49:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:49:45.00,0:49:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiho Team, what about the next batter?
Dialogue: 10,0:49:47.92,0:49:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:49:49.67,0:49:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbass! {tako}
Dialogue: 10,0:50:00.69,0:50:05.40,Thought,,0,0,0,,Still got eyes on us, huh? \NWell, we'll give ‘em one more round.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:07.98,0:50:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Try and get me! Jump!{Why is this using the "Thought" style?}{there's no way to tell if he says it out loud or not}
Dialogue: 10,0:50:12.61,0:50:15.91,Thought,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Like I'll let you keep making a fool of me! {being made to look uncool}
Dialogue: 10,0:50:17.74,0:50:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What an over-the-top dramatic play. \NIt's hard to believe we're up by three runs.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:23.08,0:50:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last one! Let's settle this!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:27.30,0:50:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pumped! {ureshi}
Dialogue: 10,0:50:31.59,0:50:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I really hit it... \NI ended up giving Batsu his moment.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:35.51,0:50:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Touch up! Send it back home! {タッチアップだ!バックホーム行くぞ!!」}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.47,0:50:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{Untranslated}{「ノーカットォ!!」}
Dialogue: 10,0:50:40.27,0:50:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Flying Cross Attack!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:42.77,0:50:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nailed it!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:43.60,0:50:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Safe!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:43.98,0:50:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit... this isn't pro wrestling, \Nit's high school baseball!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:47.77,0:50:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Kacchan, I know you'd get it too.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:50.49,0:50:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They're prepared to turn anything into a dirty brawl!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:53.07,0:50:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta crush them or they won't stop.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:55.78,0:50:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's screw them up so bad they can never play baseball again! Right, Kacchan?
Dialogue: 10,0:51:04.33,0:51:07.92,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The ninth inning's drawing to a close. Will this be Seiran's final attack?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:51:07.92,0:51:11.55,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They want to win for Haraguchi Kunio, the third baseman.
Dialogue: 10,0:51:11.55,0:51:14.43,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seiran Team has two outs, no runners.
Dialogue: 10,0:51:14.43,0:51:22.14,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seems like Kaiho's Batto-kun and Ichimonji-kun completely disrupted them. Is it just a skill difference?
Dialogue: 10,0:51:22.73,0:51:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:28.36,0:51:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:35.03,0:51:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:51:38.37,0:51:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Out!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:42.79,0:51:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon the intrusion.
Dialogue: 10,0:51:43.66,0:51:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Game set!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:45.08,0:51:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a good match.
Dialogue: 10,0:51:49.13,0:51:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:56.89,0:51:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where you headed?
Dialogue: 10,0:51:58.55,0:52:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, up the Yamanote line.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:00.06,0:52:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm off to Chinatown.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:01.85,0:52:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:04.89,0:52:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! If she's around here, \Nshe's gotta be at Yamashita Park!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:37.76,0:52:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hey, did you see my big plays?"
Dialogue: 10,0:52:41.39,0:52:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Big plays? Chinatown's that way! {meaning he didn't go where he said he would, "what is boku" means "why are you changing subject}
Dialogue: 10,0:52:44.14,0:52:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't Yamanote either! {ここが山の手だって言うのか。}
Dialogue: 10,0:52:46.02,0:52:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Anne, let's forget about him \Nand go catch goldfishes or something.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:49.44,0:52:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hands off, you idiot! {tako ga}\NGo catch some pond fish on your own! {「タコが。一人でドジョウでもすくっ\Nてこい。}
Dialogue: 10,0:52:51.90,0:52:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne doesn't need someone like you \Nfollowing her around!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:54.94,0:52:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, leave me alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:56.03,0:52:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 10,0:52:56.70,0:52:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And you too!
Dialogue: 10,0:53:02.41,0:53:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:53:03.74,0:53:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't follow me.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:05.50,0:53:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you pushing me away?
Dialogue: 10,0:53:07.00,0:53:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not pushing anyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:53:08.25,0:53:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're planning to keep \Nrunning away like this forever, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:53:13.42,0:53:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Running away?
Dialogue: 10,0:53:14.96,0:53:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You really should've watched the game to the end.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:18.76,0:53:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunio looked so relieved and clear-headed there. {on the photo I assume}
Dialogue: 10,0:53:21.39,0:53:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! He was smiling right in that photo, \Nlike he was toasting us.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:25.89,0:53:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you two wanna celebrate, suit yourselves. \NBut I don't want to be near you!
Dialogue: 10,0:53:31.02,0:53:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 10,0:53:33.48,0:53:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne! Why did you ditch that bike anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:53:38.24,0:53:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it to get over it?
Dialogue: 10,0:53:40.16,0:53:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think throwing away that bike \Nwould make you forget everything?
Dialogue: 10,0:53:42.99,0:53:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 10,0:53:48.58,0:53:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go picking up girls?
Dialogue: 10,0:53:53.38,0:53:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne!
Dialogue: 10,0:53:57.55,0:53:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sachi?
Dialogue: 10,0:53:58.67,0:53:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:53:59.34,0:54:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I borrow your bike?
Dialogue: 10,0:54:00.59,0:54:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:01.76,0:54:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 10,0:54:02.34,0:54:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I parked it by the sidewalk over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:03.93,0:54:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:04.60,0:54:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne! Are you sure you should\Nride it dressed like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:54:39.55,0:54:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne!
Dialogue: 10,0:54:40.88,0:54:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoohoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:54:43.26,0:54:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne!
Dialogue: 10,0:54:45.39,0:54:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Anne?
Dialogue: 10,0:54:48.47,0:54:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I slipped up.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:50.60,0:54:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne, maybe you shouldn't ride this bike?
Dialogue: 10,0:54:54.65,0:54:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:54:56.98,0:54:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's dangerous, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:59.73,0:55:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:04.49,0:55:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just a little mistake. \NI'm actually good at this.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:09.70,0:55:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, really!
Dialogue: 10,0:55:13.16,0:55:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I love riding! \NI'll never quit biking.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:21.26,0:55:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You might as well quit baseball.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:24.55,0:55:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne, I've decided to get my motorcycle license.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:28.22,0:55:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:55:29.72,0:55:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll keep it a secret from the baseball club.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:33.48,0:55:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.80,0:55:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.31,0:55:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne...
Dialogue: 10,0:55:38.48,0:55:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunio!
Dialogue: 10,0:55:57.58,0:56:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that—she actually jumped in herself...
Dialogue: 10,0:56:00.42,0:56:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it helps to cool your head off \Nafter getting worked up,
Dialogue: 10,0:56:03.88,0:56:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's much cheaper than ditching the bike.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:07.55,0:56:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I always thought something like this might happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:11.14,0:56:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you're walking straight ahead, \Nbut your footing's shaky.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:18.40,0:56:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This bike is shot...
Dialogue: 10,0:56:20.02,0:56:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I really have to pity this bike.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:22.40,0:56:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta treat it better. \NMy poor, poor thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:56:30.16,0:56:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least she's alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:32.99,0:56:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose. \NLuck was on her side.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:35.41,0:56:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you don't take care \Nof yourself, luck won't last.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:39.71,0:56:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,People who take care of themselves \Nalso take care of their bikes.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:43.80,0:56:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, really? \NYou're so smart, bud!
Dialogue: 10,0:57:12.28,0:57:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,People who take care of themselves \Nalso take care of their bikes.
Dialogue: 10,0:57:25.34,0:57:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it or not, that's not the point.
Dialogue: 10,0:57:27.55,0:57:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you understand what it means \Nto take care of yourself, we'll meet again.
Dialogue: 10,0:57:31.87,0:57:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,See you, Anne.
Dialogue: 10,0:57:33.43,0:57:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Be well.
Dialogue: 10,0:57:48.86,0:57:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:57:50.15,0:57:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A package for Shiraki-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:58:05.59,0:58:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fireworks leave this emptiness inside you when they stop.
Dialogue: 10,0:58:08.42,0:58:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they really let you feel both the joy \Nof meeting someone and the sadness of parting.
Dialogue: 10,0:58:16.60,0:58:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:58:20.44,0:58:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, isn't that Tacchan's lackey?
Dialogue: 10,0:58:22.40,0:58:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna watch fireworks, \Ngo somewhere else. {「花火ならどっかよそで見な」}
Dialogue: 10,0:58:24.36,0:58:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm alone!
Dialogue: 10,0:58:25.44,0:58:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you acting tough for all by yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:58:27.44,0:58:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! We've got your woman, you get that?
Dialogue: 10,0:58:29.90,0:58:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:58:30.49,0:58:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! I only came here \Nto deliver a message from Tatsuo-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:58:50.72,0:58:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to do it to you, but I bear you no grudge. \NIf you want someone to hate, save it for those two.
Dialogue: 10,0:58:56.18,0:59:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? This is useless. There's no way those two will come for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:59:01.52,0:59:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They {\i1}will{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}come.
Dialogue: 10,0:59:03.52,0:59:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you want to do with them, \Nbut they have nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:59:08.27,0:59:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get it. Whether they're involved or not, \Nthey're coming. That's just how they are.
Dialogue: 10,0:59:18.33,0:59:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And once they show up, I'll make sure they can never play baseball again.
Dialogue: 10,0:59:22.29,0:59:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 10,0:59:24.08,0:59:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't stand the way those guys\Nare playing sports. I simply can't take it!
Dialogue: 10,0:59:29.55,0:59:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What on Earth are you saying? \NIt's {\i1}you{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}who's not normal! {? dunno maybe she says "aren't they doing it the normal way"; it's different from the script: 一体なんなのそれは、正気じゃないわ}
Dialogue: 10,0:59:32.88,0:59:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! They've strayed from the path of men.
Dialogue: 10,0:59:35.72,0:59:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who doesn't get it. They—
Dialogue: 10,0:59:39.39,0:59:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Batsu and Terry are...
Dialogue: 10,0:59:57.57,0:59:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The messengers of justice have arrived!
Dialogue: 10,0:59:59.78,1:00:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are—the Battery!
Dialogue: 10,1:00:01.29,1:00:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Batsu, Terry, stay away!
Dialogue: 10,1:00:04.66,1:00:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,An off-season Santa Claus has arrived!
Dialogue: 10,1:00:07.13,1:00:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne, we're gonna save ya!
Dialogue: 10,1:00:09.04,1:00:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for dragging you into this mess.
Dialogue: 10,1:00:11.96,1:00:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Go back!
Dialogue: 10,1:00:20.85,1:00:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this seems intense.
Dialogue: 10,1:00:23.31,1:00:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, go home!
Dialogue: 10,1:00:25.52,1:00:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerks! Since you've embarrassed me so much in the past, now have a taste of your own medicine!
Dialogue: 10,1:00:34.03,1:00:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, start stripping where you stand!
Dialogue: 10,1:00:38.03,1:00:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Show your manly treasures to this girl! \NYou're confident, right?
Dialogue: 10,1:00:44.00,1:00:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! There's no need for something that stupid!
Dialogue: 10,1:00:46.71,1:00:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,1:00:47.42,1:00:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuo! If you want to see a man strip that badly, we'll show you anytime.
Dialogue: 10,1:00:52.42,1:00:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can start some music, \NSnap-in-Half Tacchan! {bokkin}
Dialogue: 10,1:00:54.26,1:00:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiots! \NWhy would I need that?!
Dialogue: 10,1:00:57.84,1:01:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry ours aren't crooked, Tatsuo.
Dialogue: 10,1:01:01.51,1:01:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They've done it...
Dialogue: 10,1:01:03.47,1:01:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Serves them right!
Dialogue: 10,1:01:05.98,1:01:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Anne! Don't hold back! Look!
Dialogue: 10,1:01:08.64,1:01:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is everything we've got.
Dialogue: 10,1:01:14.40,1:01:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No hiding or holding back—Ichimonji Teru...
Dialogue: 10,1:01:17.65,1:01:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And Batto Gun!
Dialogue: 10,1:01:24.99,1:01:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit... Kacchan!
Dialogue: 10,1:01:37.26,1:01:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,1:01:39.18,1:01:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay quiet!
Dialogue: 10,1:01:48.18,1:01:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just playing with us like rag dolls... {?? 「むう、やりたいだけやりやがって but idk what he means}
Dialogue: 10,1:01:51.31,1:01:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,1:01:53.31,1:01:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do more, come on!
Dialogue: 10,1:01:55.48,1:01:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 10,1:01:56.82,1:02:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk about the way of men, \Nyet you can't do anything yourself!
Dialogue: 10,1:02:00.24,1:02:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 10,1:02:16.96,1:02:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Coward! You're nothing but trash!
Dialogue: 10,1:02:19.76,1:02:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Do you even care what happens?!
Dialogue: 10,1:02:21.76,1:02:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead! If it makes you feel better!
Dialogue: 10,1:02:25.85,1:02:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Coward!
Dialogue: 10,1:02:27.18,1:02:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,1:02:32.90,1:02:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuo!
Dialogue: 10,1:02:44.78,1:02:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?! {???? nothing in the script}
Dialogue: 10,1:02:46.99,1:02:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Put on your pants at least, \Nit's the least a man should do. {manners; etiquette}
Dialogue: 10,1:03:02.93,1:03:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's shooting at us!
Dialogue: 10,1:03:06.60,1:03:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuo!
Dialogue: 10,1:03:08.06,1:03:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You did something you shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 10,1:03:10.27,1:03:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pretend you didn't hear me! {different from the script and idk what he says here; script: 聞いたふりな事言うな!}
Dialogue: 10,1:03:13.77,1:03:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Tatsuo!
Dialogue: 10,1:03:19.15,1:03:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump, Anne!
Dialogue: 10,1:03:32.16,1:03:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kacchan!
Dialogue: 10,1:03:33.37,1:03:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 10,1:03:34.61,1:03:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tacchan!
Dialogue: 10,1:03:40.34,1:03:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's get Anne back.
Dialogue: 10,1:03:42.51,1:03:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell do you think—
Dialogue: 10,1:03:43.88,1:03:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in my way!
Dialogue: 10,1:03:47.18,1:03:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm left-handed, anyways! {「俺は左ききなんだぁ!!」 - he hit andre with his right first and that didn't have any effect so now he's making up an excuse for it, saying "i'm a southpaw, [that's why you didn't even flinch at my hit with my right earlier]"}
Dialogue: 10,1:04:09.20,1:04:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's serious! \NHe's seriously trying to kill us!
Dialogue: 10,1:04:28.39,1:04:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,1:04:29.39,1:04:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 10,1:04:30.81,1:04:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna run you over! {/ram you - 「ぶつかるぞー}
Dialogue: 10,1:04:33.10,1:04:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rescue Squad's here!
Dialogue: 10,1:04:35.98,1:04:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kacchan! Get it together! They're escaping!
Dialogue: 10,1:04:45.40,1:04:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, my bad.
Dialogue: 10,1:04:46.78,1:04:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Anne, a gift from Batsu.
Dialogue: 10,1:04:51.83,1:04:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Asshole!
Dialogue: 10,1:05:12.89,1:05:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuo...
Dialogue: 10,1:05:15.98,1:05:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You really dumped \Na hell of a lot of extra work on us...
Dialogue: 10,1:05:26.24,1:05:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,1:05:27.36,1:05:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll live.
Dialogue: 10,1:05:39.29,1:05:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back! {退がってろ!」}
Dialogue: 10,1:05:45.75,1:05:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That... King Kong of a bastard is something...
Dialogue: 10,1:06:00.04,1:06:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... I don't have any more strength left.
Dialogue: 10,1:06:02.52,1:06:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither...
Dialogue: 10,1:06:05.11,1:06:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Batsu! Terry!
Dialogue: 10,1:06:19.58,1:06:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{??}
Dialogue: 10,1:06:34.09,1:06:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a spectacular jump. \NYou didn't even fall into the sea this time.
Dialogue: 10,1:06:42.23,1:06:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiots...
Dialogue: 10,1:06:54.95,1:06:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we should call an ambulance after all.
Dialogue: 10,1:06:56.95,1:06:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 10,1:06:58.33,1:07:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just stay like this a little longer.
Dialogue: 10,1:07:01.00,1:07:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I want to stay here too.
Dialogue: 10,1:07:05.21,1:07:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The stars are beautiful, and the wind feels good.
Dialogue: 10,1:07:11.84,1:07:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 10,1:07:19.35,1:07:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Tomorrow's the final... \Nor, well, it's today already.
Dialogue: 10,1:07:22.89,1:07:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! In that shape...
Dialogue: 10,1:07:24.98,1:07:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm joking.
Dialogue: 10,1:07:26.23,1:07:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Youth is precious; \Nyou can't just gamble it all on baseball.
Dialogue: 10,1:07:34.74,1:07:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunio's youth was all about baseball.
Dialogue: 10,1:07:38.20,1:07:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He worked hard aiming for Koshien.
Dialogue: 10,1:07:47.25,1:07:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't interested in baseball.
Dialogue: 10,1:07:51.59,1:07:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He was willing to adjust to me...
Dialogue: 10,1:07:54.55,1:07:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I liked bikes, he went through a lot of trouble to get his license.
Dialogue: 10,1:08:02.60,1:08:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He was clumsy...
Dialogue: 10,1:08:05.19,1:08:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But despite being bad, \Nhe always pressed forward, leading the pack... {ヘタなくせに･･････ついてこいとか言って突っ走ったあげ - lit: charged ahead saying "follow me"}
Dialogue: 10,1:08:11.15,1:08:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, he died.
Dialogue: 10,1:08:14.53,1:08:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fool.
Dialogue: 10,1:08:17.91,1:08:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He should've just stuck to baseball.
Dialogue: 10,1:08:23.16,1:08:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fool.
Dialogue: 10,1:09:07.21,1:09:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for any witnesses to the massive brawl \Nthat occurred around here last night...
Dialogue: 10,1:09:11.75,1:09:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything?
Dialogue: 10,1:09:14.34,1:09:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 10,1:09:16.01,1:09:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it can't be helped. I'll head back.
Dialogue: 10,1:09:21.60,1:09:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they're to be believed, \NI ought to let you ride my bike too.
Dialogue: 10,1:10:11.48,1:10:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Foul ball!
Dialogue: 10,1:10:12.65,1:10:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 10,1:10:20.99,1:10:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more...
Dialogue: 10,1:10:21.86,1:10:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,One more out, then a change.
Dialogue: 10,1:10:23.28,1:10:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,With a two-point deficit, there's still a chance.
Dialogue: 10,1:10:25.33,1:10:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If they score even one decisive point here, it'll be a disaster!
Dialogue: 10,1:10:29.12,1:10:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Batto and Ichimonji will come up \Nto bat in the bottom of the inning...
Dialogue: 10,1:10:32.37,1:10:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't rely on those two for anything.
Dialogue: 10,1:10:34.84,1:10:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How can they can even play baseball?!
Dialogue: 10,1:10:38.01,1:10:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been beaten up so badly... {/even in that condition}
Dialogue: 10,1:10:39.76,1:10:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's so infuriating. I swear!
Dialogue: 10,1:10:44.26,1:10:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Batsu, Terry...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.77,1:11:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Foul ball!
Dialogue: 10,1:11:02.55,1:11:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,T-The bases are loaded!
Dialogue: 10,1:11:04.59,1:11:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Koshien's slipping away!
Dialogue: 10,1:11:05.99,1:11:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two are getting expelled!
Dialogue: 10,1:11:08.12,1:11:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's the best plan. \NRight, Vice Principal?
Dialogue: 10,1:11:13.25,1:11:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I did judo in high school and college. \NI like people who never give up.
Dialogue: 10,1:11:20.38,1:11:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more out.
Dialogue: 10,1:11:21.84,1:11:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You said the same thing earlier.
Dialogue: 10,1:11:23.51,1:11:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Look above the Kanagawa sign. {lit: girl from kanagawa}
Dialogue: 10,1:11:24.93,1:11:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,1:11:28.85,1:11:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A mirage... my eyes are getting blurry.
Dialogue: 10,1:11:41.03,1:11:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's better. I'm ready to pitch!
Dialogue: 10,1:11:45.49,1:11:47.49,Thought,,0,0,0,,Batsu, Terry, do your best!
Dialogue: 10,1:11:47.49,1:11:50.70,Thought,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened, \Nbut let's go to Koshien together!
Dialogue: 10,1:12:06.01,1:12:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Out!
Dialogue: 10,1:12:07.80,1:12:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Three outs, change!
Dialogue: 10,1:12:12.06,1:12:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That was thrilling... {I've woken up now.}
Dialogue: 10,1:12:15.02,1:12:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,These two are something else.
Dialogue: 10,1:12:17.90,1:12:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They can be a handful, \Nbut they know exactly what's truly important.
Dialogue: 10,1:12:27.87,1:12:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally the last inning.
Dialogue: 10,1:12:30.03,1:12:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,1:12:30.62,1:12:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Kazu, can they overcome a two-point deficit?
Dialogue: 10,1:12:33.08,1:12:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Who knows...
Dialogue: 10,1:12:34.62,1:12:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No way they can, ain't that right?!
Dialogue: 10,1:12:43.67,1:12:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you? \NYou're like a feeble old man.
Dialogue: 10,1:12:47.38,1:12:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're like a rotten mummy.
Dialogue: 10,1:12:50.10,1:12:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you okay?
Dialogue: 10,1:12:51.47,1:12:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you're talking to?! \NI told you, you're ten years too young.
Dialogue: 10,1:12:55.52,1:13:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry... Batsu, it's your turn at bat. \NTwo outs, runners on first and second.
Dialogue: 10,1:13:03.57,1:13:06.90,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cleanup batter—Batto Gun, the pitcher. {???? can't hear shit, not in script}
Dialogue: 10,1:13:07.74,1:13:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Batsu, let me have a turn too.
Dialogue: 10,1:13:10.91,1:13:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't state the obvious. I'll make it to base \Nno matter what, so let me do it.
Dialogue: 10,1:13:15.62,1:13:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't state the obvious...
Dialogue: 10,1:13:17.33,1:13:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, guys...
Dialogue: 10,1:13:21.63,1:13:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Strike!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:28.80,1:13:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Strike two!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:40.65,1:13:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Batsu!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:44.44,1:13:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! D-Dead ball!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:47.19,1:13:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to first.
Dialogue: 10,1:13:48.20,1:13:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:50.24,1:13:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Bases loaded, vice principal!
Dialogue: 10,1:13:57.08,1:13:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 10,1:13:59.12,1:14:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't afford to mess this up.
Dialogue: 10,1:14:04.96,1:14:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Get it together, Terry!
Dialogue: 10,1:14:08.84,1:14:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Was my twist too weak, maybe...? {「ひねりがあまかったかな」 idk what he means}
Dialogue: 10,1:14:11.97,1:14:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Terry! Give me back my turn!
Dialogue: 10,1:14:15.68,1:14:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Terry, hold it together! {????? not in script}
Dialogue: 10,1:14:17.22,1:14:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Terry! You're sloppy! \NDon't mess around—show me baseball! {lit: show me your not half-assed baseball}
Dialogue: 10,1:14:23.90,1:14:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Terry! Terry! Terry!
Dialogue: 10,1:14:33.82,1:14:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Right-center field! { 右中間だ!}
Dialogue: 10,1:14:42.25,1:14:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it! He made it through!
Dialogue: 10,1:14:48.76,1:14:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,One more! One more and it's Koshien!
Dialogue: 10,1:14:55.68,1:14:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Batsu! Third base is right in front!
Dialogue: 10,1:14:58.18,1:14:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,1:15:01.81,1:15:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Batsu! One more step!
Dialogue: 10,1:15:10.53,1:15:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of the rest, Batsu... {dunno, maybe "I got the rest covered"}
Dialogue: 10,1:15:16.28,1:15:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Batsu! Fight!
Dialogue: 10,1:15:17.91,1:15:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 10,1:15:18.87,1:15:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Can he even run?
Dialogue: 10,1:15:22.83,1:15:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Batsu! Run!
Dialogue: 10,1:15:25.46,1:15:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Batsu! Run, you bastard!
Dialogue: 10,1:15:36.85,1:15:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 10,1:16:13.01,1:16:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Safe!
Dialogue: 10,1:16:21.60,1:16:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it! He really did it!
Dialogue: 10,1:16:27.56,1:16:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Terry!
Dialogue: 10,1:16:28.40,1:16:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They've done it!
Dialogue: 10,1:16:34.40,1:16:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{in script: well done, really well done}{Is this gonna be subbed in?}{eh nah}
Dialogue: 10,1:16:44.12,1:16:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get them someday.
Dialogue: 10,1:17:06.02,1:17:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Even if you kill him, \Nhe won't die, you know. Right?
Dialogue: 10,1:17:11.19,1:17:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You heartless bastard. \NLike hell I'll kick it before you do!
Dialogue: 10,1:17:14.99,1:17:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like I said, youth is always extreme!
Dialogue: 10,1:17:20.87,1:17:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,1:17:23.87,1:17:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously! {imo}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:51.99,0:09:58.29,Song,,0,0,0,,{心の中のFollow Wind by スターダストレビュー; have full lyrics}{乾いた昼下がりの街角\N別れを決めたばかりの二人\N軌跡を信じ続けるように\N見つめた悲しみ深い瞳\Nときめき出した胸の奥は\Nもう止まらない\N\NFollow Wind\Nもう一度愛し合える\NFollow Wind\N心から無邪気に\Nすれ違う生き方もすべて\NFollow Wind\Nせつなさを確かめ合い\NFollow Wind\N追い風にあおられ\Nこの街にこの夢に戻る\NFollow Wind\N\N愛することが下手な二人は\N都会の明かりに溶けてしまう\N指先濡らして風を見れば\N優しさ見失うこともない\N気づいたらそっと腕の中へ\Nもう離さない\N\NFollow Wind\N想い出の波を越えて\NFollow Wind\N心から素直に\N打ち明ける愛しさをすべて\NFollow Wind\N走り去る時の中へ\NFollow Wind\N追い風にあおられ\N抱きしめて捕まえていたい\NFollow Wind\N\NFollow Wind\Nもう一度愛し合える\NFollow Wind\N心から無邪気に\Nすれ違う生き方もすべて\NFollow Wind\Nせつなさを確かめ合い\NFollow Wind\N追い風にあおられ\Nこの街にこの夢に戻る\NFollow Wind}On a dry street corner in the afternoon,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.29,0:10:04.50,Song,,0,0,0,,The two who just decided to break up
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.56,0:10:11.01,Song,,0,0,0,,As if continuing to believe in their path,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.01,0:10:17.30,Song,,0,0,0,,they gazed into each other's sad eyes
Dialogue: 5,0:10:17.30,0:10:31.15,Song,,0,0,0,,The pounding in their hearts can no longer be stopped
Dialogue: 5,0:10:31.15,0:10:31.69,Song,,0,0,0,,Follow Wind
Dialogue: 5,0:10:31.69,0:10:37.87,Song,,0,0,0,,We can love each other again, with all our hearts, innocently
Dialogue: 5,0:10:37.87,0:10:43.25,Song,,0,0,0,,All the ways we pass each other by {dunno}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.91,0:10:44.58,Song,,0,0,0,,Follow Wind
Dialogue: 5,0:10:44.58,0:10:59.89,Song,,0,0,0,,We face our sadness together, and, driven by the tailwind, \Nwe return to this town and this dream {?????}
Dialogue: 5,0:28:06.41,0:28:12.25,Song,,0,0,0,,{「Lonely ≠ Story」by スターダスト☆レビュー; full lyrics found}{Lonely 出逢えるなら Story\N恋の Chance いつも 待ち続けているよ\NLonely 出逢うまでの Story\N恋は今素敵な物語になる\N\Nうつり気な月が 長い影つくり\N忘れかけた想い出 呼びもどすのさ\N涙を浮かべて ブラインド越しに\N夜のしじま 見つめていた\N\N明日の風に 淡い予感 感じたなら 今夜は\N胸にかかった 暗い雲も 遠く流れ 消えるよ\N\NLonely 悲しむのも Story\Nだから漂うのさ 風に身をまかせて\NLonely 気のすむまで Story\Nいつか覚める夢を 見るのさ このまま\N\N恋する気持ちは いたずらなものさ\Nときめくほど こんなに切なくさせる\N手が届きそうな 君の幻に\N眠れぬ夜 くり返すよ\N\N時の流れが迷いかけた この心にささやく\Nほんの少しの すれ違いは 優しさまでなくした\N\NLonely 出逢えるなら Story\N恋の Chance いつも 待ち続けているよ\NLonely 出逢うまでの Story\N恋は今すてきな物語になる}Lonely, if we could meet, Story
Dialogue: 5,0:28:12.36,0:28:19.84,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm always waiting for a chance to fall in love
Dialogue: 5,0:28:21.05,0:28:26.77,Song,,0,0,0,,Lonely, the story of how we met
Dialogue: 5,0:28:26.77,0:28:33.69,Song,,0,0,0,,Love now becomes a wonderful story
Dialogue: 5,0:28:34.86,0:28:41.62,Song,,0,0,0,,The fickle moon casts long shadows,
Dialogue: 5,0:28:42.28,0:28:49.00,Song,,0,0,0,,bringing back memories I'd almost forgotten
Dialogue: 5,0:28:49.00,0:29:02.64,Song,,0,0,0,,With tears in my eyes, I gazed through the blinds into the silence of the night
Dialogue: 5,0:29:14.42,0:29:20.53,Song,,0,0,0,,Lonely, if we could meet, story
Dialogue: 5,0:29:20.57,0:29:27.87,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm always waiting for a chance to fall in love
Dialogue: 5,0:29:27.87,0:29:29.50,Song,,0,0,0,,{ow ow ow}
Dialogue: 5,0:29:29.50,0:29:35.27,Song,,0,0,0,,Lonely, the story of how we met
Dialogue: 5,0:29:35.27,0:29:42.05,Song,,0,0,0,,Love now becomes a wonderful story
Dialogue: 5,0:31:08.55,0:31:16.85,Song,,0,0,0,,{アンのテーマREFLECTION by 作詩:平野肇 作曲:三谷泰弘 編曲:矢野立美 歌:北代桃子}{full lyrics from marty's LP photo: 都会を映す海は\N哀しいほど静かね\Nあなたを想うたびに\Nこの棧橋にくるの\N密かに燃えてた心 何故か言えずに\N振り向くように愛に気づいて\N唇がふるえる\N振り向くようにあなた探して\Nあの笑顔もうない\N晴れてる日にはきっと\Nふたりここに来たから\N今でもあなたの声\N確かに聴こえて来る} The sea reflecting the city
Dialogue: 5,0:31:16.85,0:31:24.70,Song,,0,0,0,,is so quiet it's sad
Dialogue: 5,0:31:25.07,0:31:41.84,Song,,0,0,0,,Every time I think of you, I come to this pier
Dialogue: 5,0:31:42.38,0:31:58.56,Song,,0,0,0,,My heart was secretly burning, \Nbut for some reason I couldn't put it into words
Dialogue: 5,0:31:59.40,0:32:14.16,Song,,0,0,0,,As I turned around, I realized my love, and my lips trembled
Dialogue: 5,0:32:15.96,0:32:31.85,Song,,0,0,0,,As I turned around, I searched for you, but that smile is gone
Dialogue: 5,0:33:14.51,0:33:20.85,Song,,0,0,0,,{バツのテーマ TAKE IT EASY by 作詩:川崎雅水 作曲・編曲:矢野立美 歌:GASUI; seems to only use the chorus from the song, lyrics from marty's lp photo: Take it easy Take it easy\Nうつろな時を抜けて\NTake it easy それぞれに\N笑顔は無駄じゃない\NTake it easy Take it easy\N来る日の日射し見つめ\NTake it easy いつの日か\N笑い合えるさ Hey Lover} Take it easy, take it easy\NEscape from the empty time
Dialogue: 5,0:33:20.85,0:33:26.19,Song,,0,0,0,,Take it easy, each of our smiles is not wasted
Dialogue: 5,0:33:27.15,0:33:32.62,Song,,0,0,0,,Take it easy, take it easy\NGazing at the sunlight of the coming day
Dialogue: 5,0:33:32.66,0:33:41.58,Song,,0,0,0,,Take it easy, someday\NWe'll be able to laugh together, hey lover
Dialogue: 5,0:36:21.16,0:36:30.79,Song,,0,0,0,,{DOWNTOWN STEP by 作時:平野 作曲:三谷泰弘 編曲:矢野立美 歌:スターダスト・レビュー&北代桃子; have full lyrics from marty's lp pic: (男) ひとりでいるより バスに乗りこんで\N淋しい午後行こうよ\NDowntown\Nポケットの中の コインも弾んで\N夢さえ買えそうなペイヴメント\Nみち\N(女) レンガ色の歩道 吹き抜ける予感\N足も軽くなる Downtown\Nなにかいいことがありそうね\Nあなたのやさしさのせい?\Nとき\N(男女) 大切な青春に 立ち止まっちゃ駄目さ\Nときめき続けて\NDowntown\N気の合う同士でにぎやかに\Nパーティーをさぁ始めよう\N(男) 街角を飾る バザールはいつも\N君を誘ってるのさ Downtown\Nわら\Nもっとはしゃぎなよ もっと微笑いなよ\Nまぶしい君が一番さ\N(男女) 今の愉しさだけが\Nすべてじゃないことは知っているけど\N(女) あなたの瞳に素顔を映して\N腕を絡ませて\NDowntown\N(男女) 気の合う同士でにぎやかに\Nパーティーをさぁ始めよう\N恋人のように踊ろうよ\N息の合ったステップで}Rather than being alone, let's hop on the bus
Dialogue: 5,0:36:30.79,0:36:39.05,Song,,0,0,0,,and head downtown on a lonely afternoon
Dialogue: 5,0:36:40.80,0:36:50.06,Song,,0,0,0,,The coins in my pocket are bouncing
Dialogue: 5,0:36:50.06,0:36:59.45,Song,,0,0,0,,Even dreams can be bought on this pavement
Dialogue: 5,0:37:06.16,0:37:16.46,Song,,0,0,0,,A premonition blowing through the brick-colored sidewalk,\Neven my feet feel lighter downtown
Dialogue: 5,0:37:18.01,0:37:23.14,Song,,0,0,0,,Something good seems like it's going to happen
Dialogue: 5,0:37:23.14,0:37:29.27,Song,,0,0,0,,Is it thanks to your kindness?
Dialogue: 5,0:37:30.06,0:37:40.74,Song,,0,0,0,,Don't let anyone stop you in your precious youth, \Nkeep your heart racing downtown {lyrics say seishun but it's furigana'd as toki}
Dialogue: 5,0:37:41.53,0:37:46.62,Song,,0,0,0,,Let's get the party started
Dialogue: 5,0:37:46.62,0:37:52.58,Song,,0,0,0,,with a lively bunch of like-minded people!
Dialogue: 5,0:38:04.26,0:38:09.68,Song,,0,0,0,,The bazaars decorating
Dialogue: 5,0:38:10.39,0:38:15.15,Song,,0,0,0,,the street corners
Dialogue: 5,0:38:16.57,0:38:25.62,Song,,0,0,0,,are always inviting you downtown
Dialogue: 5,0:38:28.33,0:38:33.50,Song,,0,0,0,,Have more fun,
Dialogue: 5,0:38:34.42,0:38:39.67,Song,,0,0,0,,laugh more
Dialogue: 5,0:38:40.42,0:38:50.72,Song,,0,0,0,,You're the best, dazzling
Dialogue: 5,0:38:53.56,0:39:15.37,Song,,0,0,0,,I know that the fun we have now isn't everything
Dialogue: 5,0:39:19.09,0:39:29.51,Song,,0,0,0,,My true self is reflected in your eyes, \Nand my arm is wrapped around yours downtown
Dialogue: 5,0:39:31.02,0:39:41.86,Song,,0,0,0,,Let's start a lively party with like-minded people
Dialogue: 5,0:39:42.69,0:39:45.57,Song,,0,0,0,,Let's dance
Dialogue: 5,0:39:45.57,0:39:54.71,Song,,0,0,0,,like lovers, with synchronized steps
Dialogue: 5,1:14:12.59,1:14:24.90,Song,,0,0,0,,{this is 心の中のFOLLOW WIND again but either I'm going deaf or the lyrics are completely different}{愛することが下手な二人は\N都会の明かりに溶けてしまう\N指先濡らして風を見れば\N優しさ見失うこともない\N気づいたらそっと腕の中へ\Nもう離さない}Two people who are bad at loving will melt away in the city lights
Dialogue: 5,1:14:24.90,1:14:37.70,Song,,0,0,0,,If you wet your fingertips to tell where the wind blows, \Nyou will never lose sight of kindness
Dialogue: 5,1:14:37.70,1:14:44.25,Song,,0,0,0,,When you realize it, gently take it into your arms
Dialogue: 5,1:14:46.67,1:14:51.76,Song,,0,0,0,,and never let it go
Dialogue: 5,1:14:51.76,1:15:04.10,Song,,0,0,0,,{Follow Wind\N想い出の波を越えて\NFollow Wind\N心から素直に\N打ち明ける愛しさをすべて\NFollow Wind\N走り去る時の中へ\NFollow Wind\N追い風にあおられ\N抱きしめて捕まえていたい\NFollow Wind}Follow Wind, across the waves of memories,\NI confess all my love honestly from my heart
Dialogue: 5,1:15:04.10,1:15:18.87,Song,,0,0,0,,Follow Wind, as time passes by, \NI want to embrace it and never let go, pushed by the tailwind
Dialogue: 5,1:16:42.66,1:16:48.46,Song,,0,0,0,,{スターダスト☆レビュー's Lonely≒Story again}{Lonely 出逢えるなら Story\N恋の Chance いつも 待ち続けているよ\NLonely 出逢うまでの Story\N恋は今素敵な物語になる\N\Nうつり気な月が 長い影つくり\N忘れかけた想い出 呼びもどすのさ\N涙を浮かべて ブラインド越しに\N夜のしじま 見つめていた\N\N明日の風に 淡い予感 感じたなら 今夜は\N胸にかかった 暗い雲も 遠く流れ 消えるよ\N\NLonely 悲しむのも Story\Nだから漂うのさ 風に身をまかせて\NLonely 気のすむまで Story\Nいつか覚める夢を 見るのさ このまま\N\N恋する気持ちは いたずらなものさ\Nときめくほど こんなに切なくさせる\N手が届きそうな 君の幻に\N眠れぬ夜 くり返すよ\N\N時の流れが迷いかけた この心にささやく\Nほんの少しの すれ違いは 優しさまでなくした\N\NLonely 出逢えるなら Story\N恋の Chance いつも 待ち続けているよ\NLonely 出逢うまでの Story\N恋は今すてきな物語になる}Lonely, the story of our meeting
Dialogue: 5,1:16:48.46,1:16:54.80,Song,,0,0,0,,Love now becomes a wonderful story
Dialogue: 5,1:16:56.68,1:17:11.19,Song,,0,0,0,,The fickle moon casts long shadows, bringing back memories I'd almost forgotten
Dialogue: 5,1:17:11.19,1:17:25.58,Song,,0,0,0,,With tears in my eyes, I gazed through the blinds \Ninto the silence of the night
Dialogue: 5,1:17:26.41,1:17:40.39,Song,,0,0,0,,If I feel a faint premonition in the wind of tomorrow,
Dialogue: 5,1:17:40.39,1:17:55.53,Song,,0,0,0,,the dark clouds hanging over my heart tonight \Nwill drift away and disappear.
Dialogue: 5,1:17:55.53,1:18:01.32,Song,,0,0,0,,Lonely, sadness is also a story
Dialogue: 5,1:18:01.32,1:18:08.79,Song,,0,0,0,,So I drift along, letting myself be carried away by the wind
Dialogue: 5,1:18:10.12,1:18:15.80,Song,,0,0,0,,Lonely, until I'm satisfied, story
Dialogue: 5,1:18:15.80,1:18:22.68,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll keep dreaming like this until I wake up someday
Dialogue: 5,1:18:23.89,1:18:31.27,Song,,0,0,0,,Love is mischievous
Dialogue: 5,1:18:31.27,1:18:38.53,Song,,0,0,0,,The more my heart flutters, the more painful it becomes
Dialogue: 5,1:18:38.53,1:18:52.92,Song,,0,0,0,,The illusion of you, so close I can reach out, keeps bringing me sleepless nights
Dialogue: 5,1:18:53.67,1:19:08.27,Song,,0,0,0,,The flow of time whispers to my heart that's beginning to wander
Dialogue: 5,1:19:08.27,1:19:23.07,Song,,0,0,0,,A slight misunderstanding has even taken away my kindness
Dialogue: 5,1:19:37.38,1:19:43.22,Song,,0,0,0,,Lonely, if we could meet, story
Dialogue: 5,1:19:43.22,1:19:50.68,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm always waiting for my chance at love
Dialogue: 5,1:19:52.10,1:19:57.73,Song,,0,0,0,,Lonely, until we meet, story
Dialogue: 5,1:19:57.73,1:20:05.74,Song,,0,0,0,,Love will now become a wonderful story
